{"tid":1895460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列5: 不寒而慄！中國境外疫情惡化 道瓊期貨暴跌逾700點","createTime":"2020-02-24T14:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T22:56:58.000Z","uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db72c85180d450d5ee675495e2c97b3f35cceaa2","tid":1895460,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"由於中國境外武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 確診數激增，全球累計確診 7.9511 萬例病例、死亡 2624 人。週一 (24 日) 全球股市下跌，華爾街瘋狂拋售高風險資產。<br />\n<br />\n台北時間週一晚間 8 時 40 許，美股期貨失控暴跌，道瓊期貨下跌一度超過 800 點後，維持跌逾 700 點 ，暫報 28256.0 。道瓊所有成分股期貨下跌，蘋果領跌。標普和那指 100 期貨分別下跌逾 2.7% 和 3.2%。<br />\n<br />\n週一中國境外武漢疫情急遽惡化，截稿前，韓國新增 70 起確診，累計確診 833 例，死亡 8 例。日本不惶多讓，累計確診 850 例，死亡 3 例 (含鑽石公主號郵輪)。<br />\n<br />\n疫情持續肆虐中東地區，伊朗媒體週一驚爆，第二大聖城庫姆暴增 50 死，累計總死亡人數高達 62 人，成為中國境外死亡數最多的國家，一名議員抨擊伊朗政府試圖隱匿疫情。<br />\n<br />\n義大利是亞洲以外確診數最多的國家，累計確診 219 例，死亡 5 例，為遏止疫情持續擴大，義大利當局取消「威尼斯狂歡節」，暫停接下來多項活動，歐洲股市開盤大幅下跌，義大利 FTSE MIB 指數暴跌 4.5% 以上。<br />\n<br />\nXM 高級投資分析師 Raffi Boyadjian 近期報告顯示：「上週末，中國境外確診病例繼續增加，令整個金融市場不寒而慄，因為投資者被迫重新評估自己的觀點，即疫情的影響可能是短暫的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%92%E8%80%8C%E6%85%84-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%83%A1%E5%8C%96-%E9%81%93%E7%93%8A%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%BE700%E9%BB%9E-124532675.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AF%2592%25E8%2580%258C%25E6%2585%2584-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%258C%2596-%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2593%258A%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25B7%258C%25E9%2580%25BE700%25E9%25BB%259E-124532675.html&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=309bbbe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%92%E8%80%8C%E6%85%84-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%83%A1%E5%8C%96-%E9%81%93%E7%93%8A%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%BE700%E9%BB%9E-124532675.html</a>"},{"pid":"9928635da26ef3e632b916bed317899c6823cae3","tid":1895460,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"中國疫情已經告一段落"},{"pid":"5e7d5a5acca0a6c9b19c7a1a512639b33636285c","tid":1895460,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ERhmIM-XUAAIukw?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FERhmIM-XUAAIukw%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=2906b0f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e65d29cc2712bb6c96d53ceff6c34aab777325ea","tid":1895460,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"堅定打抗疫戰，堅決穩定社會，堅守中國特色社會主義。"},{"pid":"292317643a94e06ebfbb44d0aaa9b71ed09ba881","tid":1895460,"uid":65598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"左膠無尾BEAR (#292292) 死五毛屈手足<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601170/page/38\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601170/page/38</a><br />\n留言881開始屈手足亂打人, 但又無證據<br />\n<br />\n&quot;依家係無証據話廢老先打人， 但有証據前線打人呀， 你有片既請share出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同你say sorry&quot;"},{"pid":"eff44110951c31475d8559a78eae309a7a7cf16d","tid":1895460,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"世衞總幹事譚菜得話習大人做得好好"},{"pid":"fdf8ea09778268dbfad05ee001666bf99c509f70","tid":1895460,"uid":171611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"MPF仲可以買咩基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3bf384c5254c843fe4694dae37d235a15d3a12","tid":1895460,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"熊軍有福了"},{"pid":"a3a5